{
  "stem": "894.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And with the schooling, really it was like, I cannot say that I reached a great education at home, but right after the war, when I came to Cluj, I went back for a while, there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had an English professor who gave me courses in English.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when I came to the United States, I went to night school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then I got married and had the children, and so it took quite a few years til I went to college.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, everybody, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-Jewish and Jewish, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not the ones I associated with.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- there was a little girl I remember who was non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was very good friends with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She didn't come to my home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how my father would react to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my-- but I would go every now and then to hers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew that I cannot eat there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If they offered me any food, I would say, well, I can't, because I'm kosher, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I had one or two friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But otherwise, you were mostly with your own circle of people-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a lot of talk of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall anybody throwing a rock in our window, but I remember my mother worrying when my father would come home from shul on a Saturday, because he walked with the long beard.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and you heard incidences where young, you know, Gentile boys would throw rocks or would-- you know, it wasn't extreme.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't like a pogrom, where you were worried about, you know, having your whole family killed, at least not in my time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Towards my father, I'm not aware, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But you heard of incidences, and you knew that anti-Semitism exists.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
